The paper deals with face alignment, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of deep learning techniques such as CNN and RNN, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the computational efficiency of the proposed method, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
